The paper focuses on road scene understanding using deep learning-based segmentation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The paper also discusses the advantages and disadvantages of different CNN architectures, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper proposes a new network architecture, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE).
